305
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:45,030
Mr. Liu.

306
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:47,730
Xiaolan.

307
00:09:49,290 --> 00:09:49,910
Mr. Tang.

308
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:50,270
Well.

309
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,150
