319
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:13,910
Yes.

320
00:10:13,930 --> 00:10:15,220
Well, give them to me.

321
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,510
Inside. This way.

322
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:16,960
Welcome.

323
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,790
All right, all right.

324
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,390
Thank you.

325
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,390
Go get a bowl of mutton soup

326
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,270
