327
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:22,270
Okay.

328
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,340
Please come in.

329
00:10:23,450 --> 00:10:24,390
Inside, please.

330
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,270
Hello, folks.

331
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,740
