332
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:27,860
How should I know?

333
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:28,960
Let's go.

334
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,080
Let's go inside.

335
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,240
Granny Yu.

336
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,470
Nice to meet you.

337
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:33,670
Welcome, welcome.

338
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:35,750
Here, Mayor Tang.

339
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,670
Have some tea to warm up.

340
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:38,200
Let me get it. Let me.

341
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:38,630
I can manage.

342
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:39,570
Let me get it. Let me.

343
00:10:39,570 --> 00:10:40,030
No need to be polite.

344
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,240
Alright, thank you.

345
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:42,750
It's cold. Have some soup.

346
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,480
Mutton soup.

347
00:10:45,970 --> 00:10:47,270
Did you make this soup?

348
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,030
It's hot.

349
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:55,880
This soup

350
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,110
