363
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:17,240
After the New Year,

364
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:17,790
I plan

365
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,750
to take these folks

366
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:20,020
