374
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,000
Right.

375
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:33,320
-Yes.
-Yes, as long as we can make money.

376
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:35,080
You look familiar.

377
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,790
-You are County—
-Chief.

378
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:37,690
You can just

379
00:11:37,690 --> 00:11:39,240
