380
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,440
Anything else feels distant.

381
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:41,790
Okay.

382
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:42,510
Comrade it is.

383
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:43,790
Hello, Comrade Tang.

384
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:44,910
Sit down, Chief.

385
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:45,200
Please, sit.

386
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,440
Have some sunflower seeds, please.

387
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,100
Okay, okay.

388
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,410
No formalities.

389
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,510
We're all friends here.

390
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:49,930
Okay, okay.

391
00:11:49,930 --> 00:11:50,720
Thank you. Thank you.

392
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,180
Thanks.

393
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:51,910
Come on.

394
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:54,240
Chief,

395
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:55,480
