400
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:03,720
Happy.

401
00:12:03,770 --> 00:12:04,320
Right?

402
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:04,720
Happy.

403
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:06,550
Delighted.

404
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:07,630
Hey, Yong.

405
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,680
Your business in Shengcheng

406
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:11,180
