407
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:11,720
No, no.

408
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:12,630
It's alright.

409
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,510
Here.

410
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,670
He drank it all.

411
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,200
Here.

412
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:24,360
Another bowl for the Mayor.

413
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:25,440
Another bowl?

414
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,670
