416
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,000
Hello?

417
00:12:44,910 --> 00:12:45,600
Zhou Cheng.

418
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,610
Xiaolan isn't here.

419
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,960
She's gone to the Chief's house.

420
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,200
Okay.

421
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:53,790
I'll tell her.

422
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,930
Everything's fine in the village.

423
00:12:58,150 --> 00:13:00,610
Some people just play matchmakers blindly.

424
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:04,000
For your future mother-in-law.

425
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:07,440
Okay.

426
00:13:08,100 --> 00:13:09,160
I'm hanging up now.

427
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,320
Don't they want to see

428
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:19,840
