430
00:13:21,430 --> 00:13:22,670
Let's show them.

431
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,270
My mom and Mr. Tang?

432
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,340
Your mom can't tell,

433
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,120
