439
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,720
Do you believe me?

440
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:40,950
I believe you. Of course.

441
00:13:40,970 --> 00:13:41,600
Granny Yu,

442
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,130
