443
00:13:43,610 --> 00:13:44,840
Come, try this.

444
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:45,810
Abalone.

445
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,440
Mr. Tang.

446
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,250
Seafood.

447
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,000
Mr. Tang.

448
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:48,480
Okay.

449
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,440
Mr. Tang.

450
00:13:50,010 --> 00:13:51,550
I don't have very nice clothes here,

451
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:52,480
but this is warm.

452
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,670
That's great, Yong.

453
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:54,840
You've solved a big problem for me.

454
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,480
Alright, as long as it's warm,

455
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,000
Mr. Tang.

456
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:57,960
Thank you. Thank you.

457
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,560
Sit, Yong.

458
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,360
Don't call me Mr. Tang.

459
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,240
We're about the same age,

460
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,510
