461
00:14:03,510 --> 00:14:04,360
Just call me Tang.

462
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,290
I wouldn't dare.

463
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,000
Why wouldn't you?

464
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,730
Call me Tang.

465
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:09,260
Barbecue pork buns are here.

466
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,080
Honey, what are these called?

467
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,510
These are barbecue pork buns.

468
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:16,440
-Barbecue pork buns?
-Barbecue pork buns?

469
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,270
A famous snack in Shengcheng.

470
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:19,750
Hey, Fen, Fen.

471
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:20,910
Give one to him.

472
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:21,870
Have him try this.

473
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:22,530
Okay, okay.

474
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:24,310
I see that today's dishes

475
00:14:24,550 --> 00:14:26,080
