478
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:28,810
In a bit,

479
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:30,800
I'll volunteer to wash the dishes.

480
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,080
Look. Just look at that.

481
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:33,480
Yong,

482
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,570
