483
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,480
Okay, okay.

484
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,670
I-I'll wash the dishes too.

485
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:37,870
Try it while it's hot.

486
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,790
Let's try it.

487
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,140
Have a taste, come on.

488
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,360
Try it, come on.

489
00:14:43,050 --> 00:14:44,170
Are you not leaving

490
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,270
tonight?

491
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:48,440
If you put it that way,

492
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,270
I'll be shameless

493
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,670
