494
00:14:52,870 --> 00:14:53,390
Fen.

495
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:54,520
Is that okay?

496
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:56,390
Um...

497
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,000
Well...

498
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,790
