499
00:14:58,790 --> 00:14:59,120
Okay,

500
00:14:59,240 --> 00:14:59,750
I'll help you.

501
00:14:59,750 --> 00:15:00,550
It's a bit hot.

502
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:01,120
Well...

503
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:01,440
Let me do it. Let me.

504
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,100
Let me do it.

505
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:02,870
Let me.

506
00:15:04,310 --> 00:15:04,970
Okay, okay.

507
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:05,750
Well...

508
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:06,410
Okay, okay.

509
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:09,220
What's going on?

510
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:11,340
What's happening?

511
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:12,740
Help me lift the curtain.

512
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:13,710
Okay, thanks.

513
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,770
Fengmei, add some soup.

514
00:15:16,590 --> 00:15:17,200
Granny Yu,

515
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,540
when did those two

516
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:20,790
