520
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,110
No way.

521
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:34,270
They don't look like a match.

522
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,030
Eat. Eat.

523
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:35,750
D-D-Don't...

524
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,870
Don't gossip.

525
00:15:36,890 --> 00:15:37,720
Drink up, come on.

526
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:38,910
-Come on.
-Come on.

527
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:40,000
Have a drink.

528
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,330
Okay.

529
00:15:40,550 --> 00:15:40,880
Okay.

530
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:43,930
I'm leaving, Yong!

531
00:15:43,930 --> 00:15:44,620
Bye, Yong!

532
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,360
Bye. Happy New Year.

533
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,550
Come visit often.

534
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,210
Come visit.

535
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:49,630
Okay. Take care.

536
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:52,750
Comrade Tang.

537
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,390
Thank you.

538
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,630
Treat this place like your own home.

539
00:15:54,630 --> 00:15:55,150
Will do.

540
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,120
Take care.

541
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:56,930
Be careful.

542
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,100
Happy New Year.

543
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:58,960
Happy New Year.

544
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,160
Take care. Take care.

545
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,010
Comrade Liu Fen.

546
00:16:08,390 --> 00:16:09,710
I'd like to have a word with you,

547
00:16:09,710 --> 00:16:10,280
