548
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:17,480
I'll get straight to the point.

549
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:18,550
We've known

550
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:19,240
each other

551
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,500
