568
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:00,330
Mayor Tang.

569
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:03,080
No, Mr. Tang.

570
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,480
Just call me Tang.

571
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:05,589
Okay.

572
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:08,270
Fen,

573
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,339
Xiaolan,

574
00:17:09,589 --> 00:17:10,750
