584
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:26,329
with the intention

585
00:17:26,859 --> 00:17:27,790
of marrying her?

586
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,560
I-I didn't mean...

587
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,240
Mr. Tang.

588
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,310
I'd like to

589
00:17:35,110 --> 00:17:36,570
