590
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:37,400
Sure.

591
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:38,850
Let's go for a walk.

592
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:39,330
Okay.

593
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:40,420
We'll take a walk.

594
00:17:48,810 --> 00:17:50,540
There's nothing wrong with it,

595
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:54,290
but it feels like everything is wrong.

596
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:02,960
Oh my goodness.

597
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:06,440
New Year in the countryside is so lively.

598
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:10,160
Cooking a whole table of food

599
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,480
made me exhausted.

600
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,480
Thanks for your hard work, Granny Yu.

601
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:14,820
Here.

602
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:15,930
Have some water.

603
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,800
We were all working hard.

604
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,560
Granny Yu.

605
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,110
Why didn't you

606
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:25,170
tell me in advance?

607
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:26,900
If I had told you first,

608
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,800
would it have worked so well?

609
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:32,070
Aren't the neighbors all watching

610
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:33,270
to see what kind of man

611
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:35,000
your mom will find?

612
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,720
Now they've seen it.

613
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,160
That shut them up.

614
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:42,680
But I think my mom

615
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:44,890
might not be able to accept it yet.

616
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:47,510
You've done enough

617
00:18:47,510 --> 00:18:49,070
to make your mom proud.

618
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,510
As for

619
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:53,110
the inferiority caused

620
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,070
by her divorce,

621
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:56,200
no one else

622
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,790
can help her.

623
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:01,130
She must walk out of it herself.

624
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,200
Now that

625
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,000
such an excellent man likes her,

626
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,960
even if they don't work out,

627
00:19:08,730 --> 00:19:09,990
at least in the future,

628
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:12,970
your mom's standards

629
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:16,070
will be higher, right?

630
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,240
I can't argue

631
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,640
with what Granny Yu said.

632
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:22,310
Even in 30 years,

633
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:26,570
there will still be people
in society who think this way:

634
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:27,750
For a woman,

635
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:30,310
no matter how successful her career is,

636
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,320
or how wonderful her life is,

637
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:34,240
if she doesn't have a marriage,

638
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,590
her life is still considered incomplete.

639
00:19:35,590 --> 00:19:36,680
You are so kind

640
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,260
to invite me over for the New Year.

641
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:41,000
I couldn't come empty-handed.

642
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:42,480
Consider this

643
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:44,350
my New Year's gift to you.

644
00:19:46,030 --> 00:19:47,350
Whether my mom can accept it

645
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:48,410
is not certain yet,

646
00:19:49,110 --> 00:19:50,480
but I understand your intentions,

647
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,200
Granny Yu.

648
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:53,080
Thank you, Granny Yu.

649
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:56,200
I didn't bring you a gift,

650
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,930
yet you're thanking me?

651
00:19:58,870 --> 00:20:00,800
Well, you are Granny Yu, after all.

652
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,030
Fen, you're back.

653
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:04,560
I'm back.

654
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:08,720
Mr. Tang.

655
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,200
I have never met

656
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,460
a leader as good as you.

657
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,720
But you are a leader,

658
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,350
who are educated,

659
00:20:18,030 --> 00:20:18,750
unlike me.

660
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:21,030
I was born in this village

661
00:20:21,030 --> 00:20:22,290
and grew up right here.

662
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:23,610
I'm not very educated.

663
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:27,030
So I think...

664
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:31,440
there is a big gap between us.

665
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,880
You and I...

666
00:20:35,070 --> 00:20:35,930
aren't really—

667
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:40,480
Did you catch a cold?

668
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:43,030
Button up your coat.

669
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:53,280
Button it up.

670
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,640
You didn't wear long johns, did you?

671
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:03,830
The village isn't like the city.

672
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,350
There are no tall buildings
to block the wind.

673
00:21:06,350 --> 00:21:08,440
It's several degrees colder
than in the city.

674
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:09,170
Coming here,

675
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,920
surely in many ways,

676
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,120
you are not used to it.

677
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:16,350
But I think this place

678
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:17,690
has good air

679
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,000
and good scenery.

680
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:21,590
What's more,

681
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,830
the people raised in the village

682
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:24,810
are even better.

683
00:21:27,770 --> 00:21:29,430
Light one. Quick. Fireworks.

684
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,490
Come on, let's do it together.

685
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:38,560
Hey, kid.

686
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:40,810
Can you give me two?

687
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:41,970
Sure, here.

688
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,400
Okay.

689
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:42,920
Here.

690
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:43,940
Thanks.

691
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,070
Let's go play over there.

692
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:46,350
Okay.

693
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,010
Be careful.

694
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,500
I'll light one too.

695
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,590
I used to do this when I was little.

696
00:21:53,590 --> 00:21:54,850
It's been so many years

697
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:56,320
since I played with this.

698
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,330
It's beautiful.

699
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:08,170
Do you want to light one too?

700
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,550
Be careful.

701
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,000
Xia.

702
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:39,480
I hustled a job managing costumes,

703
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:40,610
and I got backstage.

704
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,720
Only after I got here did I realize

705
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:45,030
that the hosts'

706
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:46,030
and the guests' costumes

707
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:47,960
had already been decided long ago.

708
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:50,680
I'm afraid it's going to be difficult
this time.

709
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,110
Don't rush to admit defeat.

710
00:22:52,110 --> 00:22:53,030
You already made it backstage.

711
00:22:53,030 --> 00:22:54,510
That's half the battle won.

712
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:56,480
As for the hosts' and guests' outfits,

713
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,960
is it certain they won't change them?

714
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:58,720
Even if they're decided,

715
00:22:58,720 --> 00:23:00,350
couldn't something go wrong later?

716
00:23:00,350 --> 00:23:01,680
If there's no opportunity,

717
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:03,160
you have to find one.

718
00:23:04,790 --> 00:23:05,510
Xia,

719
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:07,750
you mean...

720
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:09,480
I think you can try

721
00:23:09,640 --> 00:23:11,110
focusing on the artists from Gangdao.

722
00:23:11,110 --> 00:23:12,680
They might have more freedom

723
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:14,540
with their own clothing choices.

724
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:17,220
For instance, someone like Wu Kaili.

725
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:17,960
Wu Kaili?

726
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:18,640
Yes.

727
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:20,960
Alright. Good luck.

728
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:21,750
Xia.

729
00:23:26,030 --> 00:23:27,090
Done making calls?

730
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:30,170
Missing anyone?

731
00:23:32,110 --> 00:23:32,590
No.

732
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:34,790
Good.

733
00:23:43,470 --> 00:23:44,670
I didn't miss anyone.

734
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:47,920
I just haven't figured out
what to say yet.

735
00:23:50,110 --> 00:23:52,480
Hot dumplings are here!

736
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:53,270
Fengmei, sit down quickly.

737
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,350
The dumplings are ready.

738
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:55,640
Come on, come on. Let's eat together.

739
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,320
Let's all

740
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:57,510
wish Granny Yu good health.

741
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:57,830
Okay.

742
00:23:57,830 --> 00:23:58,640
-Okay?
-Okay.

743
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,680
And wish everyone a Happy New Year.

744
00:24:00,710 --> 00:24:03,790
-Happy New Year!
-May joy fill our home!

745
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:07,870
Here, Liu Fen.

746
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,040
Fen, here.

747
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,300
Let me give you a piece of chicken.

748
00:24:12,350 --> 00:24:13,410
Eat while it's hot.

749
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:15,720
Have a dumpling then.

750
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,240
Yes, you'd better eat it while it's hot.

751
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:17,640
Look.

752
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:18,960
Let me serve you.

753
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:21,880
Fengmei.

754
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:22,790
Have a dumpling.

755
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:23,450
Okay, okay.

756
00:24:23,980 --> 00:24:25,220
Mr. Tang, please eat.

757
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:25,750
Try it.

758
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:26,670
Thank you.

759
00:24:26,830 --> 00:24:27,790
Just help yourself.

760
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:28,920
Just help yourself.

761
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:31,240
Granny Yu.

762
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:33,910
I see you were rejected
by Fen, weren't you?

763
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:35,970
It wasn't exactly a rejection.

764
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:38,200
Fen just thinks

765
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:39,750
that the two of us

766
00:24:40,350 --> 00:24:42,410
aren't very suitable for each other.

767
00:24:43,070 --> 00:24:43,720
She...

768
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:48,480
I still want to thank you

769
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:49,350
for calling me.

770
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:53,140
That's because you have guts.

771
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:53,870
Thank you.

772
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:55,160
Keep trying.

773
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:56,270
I will.

774
00:24:58,960 --> 00:24:59,490
Xiaolan.

775
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,110
Dear friends,

776
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,200
comrades,

777
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:08,160
the Year of the Snake Spring Festival Gala

778
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:10,750
officially begins now.

779
00:25:13,510 --> 00:25:14,880
As we bid farewell to the old
and welcome the new,

780
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:15,640
in this wonderful moment,

781
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:16,960
we gather here happily.

782
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:17,490
Xiaolan,

783
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,920
they aren't using

784
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:19,920
our Luna clothes.

785
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:21,510
Don't worry. It has just started.

786
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:22,440
Let's eat first.

787
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,030
Right, right.

788
00:25:23,030 --> 00:25:23,720
They'll definitely be there.

789
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:24,270
Let's have another drink.

790
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:24,750
Let's toast to Granny Yu again.

791
00:25:24,750 --> 00:25:25,590
Wish Granny Yu good health

792
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:26,400
and a long life.

793
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,000
Great.

794
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:30,200
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

795
00:26:01,670 --> 00:26:02,350
Wei.

796
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:03,780
Where is Cheng?

797
00:26:04,590 --> 00:26:05,440
Happy New Year.

798
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,030
Happy New Year.

799
00:26:06,030 --> 00:26:06,640
Cheng.

800
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:08,070
Cheng.

801
00:26:08,340 --> 00:26:09,510
Come back for dumplings.

802
00:26:09,510 --> 00:26:09,920
Okay.

803
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:15,160
Fish is here.

804
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:20,030
Grandma,

805
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:22,080
you look so beautiful.

806
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:24,200
You are never serious.

807
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:25,590
Tell me,

808
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:26,550
next year,

809
00:26:26,830 --> 00:26:28,200
can you find a boyfriend

810
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,160
and bring him home for the New Year?

811
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,070
Grandma.

812
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:31,240
Okay, okay.

813
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,640
No problem.

814
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,310
No problem.

815
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:46,030
One more?

816
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:46,510
Okay.

817
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:48,690
These two

818
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,450
rarely see each other all year.

819
00:26:50,910 --> 00:26:51,720
We still need to find a way

820
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,380
to move to Shengcheng sooner.

821
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,350
A family

822
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:55,680
living happily together

823
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:57,080
is what life is all about.

824
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:01,160
My brother has mentioned it
to me several times.

825
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:03,270
He said once he was done
with his current project

826
00:27:03,270 --> 00:27:04,270
and made some more money,

827
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,600
he'd bring you two over.

828
00:27:06,310 --> 00:27:07,440
To be honest,

829
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:08,720
I really can't bear to leave

830
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:10,160
the business in Jingcheng.

831
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,270
If we close the shop,

832
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:13,600
think of how much money
we'd lose in a year.

833
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,640
I want to stick it out
for a couple of years.

834
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,830
After we save enough money

835
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:18,220
and are better off.

836
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:19,750
Before long,

837
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,200
buying a commercial residential property
in Shengcheng

838
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,480
will let us
get the local household registration.

839
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:24,200
By then, it'll be convenient for Tao

840
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:24,700
to go there to study,

841
00:27:24,700 --> 00:27:25,960
without the need for temporary schooling.

842
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:26,640
Buy a house?

843
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:29,000
Don't work units allocate one?

844
00:27:29,030 --> 00:27:30,000
Why buy a house?

845
00:27:30,190 --> 00:27:31,450
Do you have a work unit?

846
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:32,830
No.

847
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:34,400
People like us without work units

848
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,460
have to buy our own.

849
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,160
Comrade Liu Fen,

850
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,090
you are getting more enlightened.

851
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:41,540
How about this?

852
00:27:41,750 --> 00:27:43,160
Give me some more time.

853
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,710
I'll buy the land

854
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:46,030
and build the house myself.

855
00:27:46,030 --> 00:27:47,000
I'll keep one floor

856
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,270
for our family to live in.

857
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:49,200
Xiaolan,

858
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:50,520
you are so capable.

859
00:27:50,550 --> 00:27:52,070
We're waiting for your big mansion.

860
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:52,590
Here.

861
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:55,960
Xiaolan!

862
00:27:56,270 --> 00:27:57,000
Your call!

863
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:57,880
Coming!

864
00:28:01,550 --> 00:28:01,950
Hello?

865
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:03,030
Xia.

866
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,350
Is the TV on?

867
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,480
Watch it, quick.

868
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,080
It worked.

869
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:09,280
Mom, Mom!

870
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,590
Auntie, come look!

871
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,720
Is this it?

872
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:15,720
What Wu Kaili is wearing

873
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,270
is our Luna clothes!

874
00:28:17,270 --> 00:28:18,160
-Yes, right.
-Really?

875
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:18,680
Isn't that

876
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,920
the singer from Gangdao?

877
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:20,320
She...

878
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:22,070
She's wearing Luna clothes!

879
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:23,480
This is Xiaolan's brand!

880
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:24,310
Yes.

881
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,680
That's great.

882
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,080
Right?

883
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:26,920
Chen,

884
00:28:27,170 --> 00:28:27,960
how did you make it?

885
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,020
That's so amazing.

886
