1104
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,180
Come on, Granny Yu. That's right.

1105
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:13,800
Don't shake the camera.

1106
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,670
Just hold it steady.

1107
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:15,400
Hold it steady.

1108
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,400
