Actually, before the New Year,

1170
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,190
I already saw them.

1171
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,000
But I ran away.

1172
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:04,320
I wasn't afraid

1173
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,280
that you would say something

1174
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:06,550
I couldn't accept.

1175
00:40:07,630 --> 00:40:09,400
It's just that when I thought about

1176
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:11,790
how a confrontation
might lead to an argument,

1177
00:40:11,790 --> 00:40:12,800
I got scared.

1178
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:17,510
Xiaolan, you might have misunderstood.

1179
00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:19,320
What you saw that day was likely

1180
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:21,440
Shi Kai's wife and son.

1181
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:26,710
Actually,

1182
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:29,390
the day you had the car accident,

1183
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,180
Shi Kai and I...

1184
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:35,920
Cheng.

1185
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,030
Is this the place?

1186
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:38,480
Should be here.

1187
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:45,760
Why would the person involved choose

1188
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:46,760
a place like this?

1189
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:55,510
Cheng,

1190
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,440
let's ask someone.

1191
00:40:59,630 --> 00:41:00,000
Okay.

1192
00:41:02,110 --> 00:41:02,810
Hello, Sir.

1193
00:41:03,720 --> 00:41:04,580
May I ask...

1194
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:50,440
How is it?

1195
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:51,840
How is it, Doctor?

1196
00:41:51,960 --> 00:41:53,490
We did everything we could.

1197
00:42:05,550 --> 00:42:06,210
Zhou Cheng.

1198
00:42:07,740 --> 00:42:08,440
Your friend just

1199
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:09,570
called the law firm,

1200
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:10,800
saying your partner was sent

1201
00:42:10,800 --> 00:42:12,730
to Shengcheng People's Hospital.

1202
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:18,230
I wanted

1203
00:42:19,030 --> 00:42:20,160
to tell you that day,

1204
00:42:21,630 --> 00:42:23,230
but when I got to the hospital

1205
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:25,720
and saw something happened to you too,

1206
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:27,760
I really didn't know

1207
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:28,480
how to say it.
